message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper involves the development of a deep learning model for fetal brain imaging using multi-view MRI and attention-based techniques. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) with medical imaging (cs.MED) and neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
